track_notes: This path is nice and easy, you need good shoes to walk on the Chalancha crest, on the way back you can climb Mont Tournairet and score a couple of points!

This is a nice walk coming from Valdeblore; i did it with snowshoes and was a bit tired at the end. No probleme in spring or summertime, get some water. plenty room on summit, but no trees for setup the antenna
long Walk to reach 2 summits Chalancha and Tournairet
